headline: 1 Large-Cap Stock to Consider Right Now and 2 Facing Challenges
summary: Large-cap stocks usually command their industries because they have the scale to drive market trends. The flip side though is that their sheer size can limit growth as expanding further becomes an increasingly challenging task.

headline: Lennar (LEN): Exploring the Homebuilder’s Valuation After Recent Share Price Momentum
summary: Lennar (LEN) shares have edged slightly higher over the past week, gaining about 6%, as investors weigh recent industry data and broader market signals. The homebuilder’s performance has outpaced the sector in the past 3 months; it has climbed 15% during that period. See our latest analysis for Lennar.
